{"tid":300771,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"城市大學環球商業學","createTime":"2017-06-28T07:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T16:58:59.000Z","uid":14799,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f2cf5eacf02c3d7891dd7366e6042110e9fc6fb","tid":300771,"uid":14799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T07:16:09.000Z","msg":"各位剛剛完成DSE的準大學生，你們好！首先恭喜你們完成了人生個一個重要里程碑，並快踏入人生另階段。現在我帶給了你們一個好消息，城市大學的精英課程-環球商業學(GBUS) 上線了！以下我為各位同學仔介紹課程特色！<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/28/150607_0892e123d6e57a76ba8179117b2bc7aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F28%2F150607_0892e123d6e57a76ba8179117b2bc7aa.jpg&h=d2aa5c03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位進入準GBUSer會有三次exchange 機會， 當中包括各世界名牌大學 例如：利物浦大學，列斯聯大學，哥本哈根商學院⋯⋯ 各大學所在地都有各自著名球會，實在係一眾球迷福氣！ 相比其他大學去Yale LSE IC 等校有過之而無不給！<br />\n<br />\n此外，各準GBUSer只要有<strong>6</strong>科28分及<strong>1</strong>科5*或以上，就可以獲得合共$80000入學合，連同各項scholarship，最多可獲$265000。有Best 5 25分嘅你，與其入三大讀文學乞食做普通人，不如入城大讀GBUS 先袋幾十萬！<br />\n<br />\nGlobal Challenges for Global Elites<br />\nWe are elites, elites, elites!"},{"pid":"366aa3404c58bd5e5095fd4fec484e8fa0802f4e","tid":300771,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T07:20:13.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"d7c97cf1f9c0435ecdc227a4551368ee41f74816","tid":300771,"uid":14799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T07:23:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>？</blockquote><br />\n巴打登死保方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我仲記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c76a8016bd06ace4f9e954eccc8276068473dc","tid":300771,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T07:23:19.000Z","msg":"其實好鬼吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一入學就八皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa